Modify the "build.xml" to update the value of "junit", maybe you also need to configure the path for dependencies.
And
1.modify
test_files\configV11.xml
test_files\db_conf.xml
test_files\DBConfig.xml
test_files\accuracy\DBConnectionFactory.xml
test_files\failure\config.xml
test_files\stress\db_conf.xml
According your Informix server setting.

2.execute
test_files\phase_management.sql

then run test.